92
00:09:33,950 --> 00:09:35,750
Thank you so much!

93
00:09:38,890 --> 00:09:41,190
I thought you must have grown up in a caring family,

94
00:09:41,730 --> 00:09:45,130
and that you had a very kind heart.

95
00:09:46,230 --> 00:09:50,000
That was why I created this place just like your home,

96
00:09:50,340 --> 00:09:53,270
so you can feel comfortable in here.

97
00:09:56,170 --> 00:09:58,740
However, you didn't even take a look at me.

98
00:09:58,740 --> 00:10:00,880
I bet you had forgotten all about me.

99
00:10:04,050 --> 00:10:07,020
