100
00:10:08,350 --> 00:10:09,760
However, I just couldn't wait any longer.

101
00:10:14,790 --> 00:10:17,560
That sounds so corny when I say it aloud.

102
00:10:21,830 --> 00:10:24,070
This might be the first time that

103
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:28,970
I've felt getting closer to him.

104
00:10:32,010 --> 00:10:36,420
I'm glad you told me.

105
00:10:38,580 --> 00:10:39,820
Really?

106
00:10:45,620 --> 00:10:49,760
But I really did fall for you at first sight.

107
00:11:03,810 --> 00:11:05,180
Mr. Fukami...

108
00:11:08,880 --> 00:11:10,250
Do you know now that

109
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:14,520
how much I like you?

110
00:11:19,930 --> 00:11:22,590
I have been dreaming the day to take you to here.

111
00:11:24,160 --> 00:11:26,470
Can we just stay here for a little longer?

112
00:11:28,630 --> 00:11:29,900
I'd love to.

113
00:11:32,900 --> 00:11:35,870
