117
00:11:53,030 --> 00:11:53,890
Slick move.

118
00:11:54,630 --> 00:11:58,400
What's the CEO of the Akutsu doing here?

119
00:11:59,900 --> 00:12:02,300
He is a CEO too.

120
00:12:02,300 --> 00:12:04,070
I'm here out of curiosity.

121
00:12:04,070 --> 00:12:08,210
I just couldn't believe Mr. Fukami would go that far to open a cafe for a woman.

122
00:12:08,410 --> 00:12:11,840
I was wondering what kind of cafe and woman it would be.

123
00:12:16,180 --> 00:12:18,680
