I'm just a normal college student.

126
00:12:42,470 --> 00:12:45,340
He might don't want people know about me.

127
00:12:47,050 --> 00:12:49,780
And I didn't really greet the other person properly.

128
00:12:54,050 --> 00:12:57,190
I'm so sorry

129
00:13:00,060 --> 00:13:05,800
for embarrassing you in front of your acquaintance

130
